---

<section id="experiencias" class="bg-[#e6ddd2] text-[#2f2a26] py-16 md:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-12">
      An experience for every traveler
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-[#e8e0d6] p-6 space-y-3">
        <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-[#edf3ec] flex items-center justify-center text-[#2f4b2c]">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" class="h-5 w-5">
            <path d="M12 12a3 3 0 1 0-3-3 3 3 0 0 0 3 3Z" />
            <path d="M4 20a6 6 0 0 1 16 0" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">For the Exploring Family</h3>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#4b463f]">
          A place where memories come easy: shared table, home-style flavor, and an atmosphere built
          to enjoy together. Here the family feels cared for, like at home.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-[#e8e0d6] p-6 space-y-3">
        <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-[#edf3ec] flex items-center justify-center text-[#2f4b2c]">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" class="h-5 w-5">
            <path d="M12 21s-7-4.35-7-10a7 7 0 1 1 14 0c0 5.65-7 10-7 10Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">For Adventurous Lovers</h3>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#4b463f]">
          Perfect plan: a day of exploring, a dinner with history, and a romantic finish in the
          thermal waters of Sueno Dorado. Tradition and connection in one trip.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-[#e8e0d6] p-6 space-y-3">
        <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-[#edf3ec] flex items-center justify-center text-[#2f4b2c]">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" class="h-5 w-5">
            <path d="M5 10h14" />
            <path d="M5 14h14" />
            <path d="M5 18h14" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">For the Zen Retiree</h3>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#4b463f]">
          Slow pace, warm attention, and comforting food. Rest here is not only physical: it is
          emotional. And the hot springs are the wellness touch that transforms the trip.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-[#e8e0d6] p-6 space-y-3">
        <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-[#edf3ec] flex items-center justify-center text-[#2f4b2c]">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" class="h-5 w-5">
            <path d="M8 10h8" />
            <path d="M8 14h4" />
            <path d="M6 5h12v14H6Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">For the Disconnected Professional</h3>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#4b463f]">
          Escape the noise without complications. Authentic food, comfort, and a setting that lowers
          the pace. Hot springs included to reset with energy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-[#e8e0d6] p-6 space-y-3">
        <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-[#edf3ec] flex items-center justify-center text-[#2f4b2c]">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" class="h-5 w-5">
            <path d="m4 11 8-7 8 7" />
            <path d="M8 14v6h8v-6" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">For Costa Ricans Proud of Our Roots</h3>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#4b463f]">
          This place is a statement of identity: rooted flavors, real history, and that way of
          welcoming you that only we have. Abuela Luisita is Costa Rica served with care.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
